{"tid":1025903,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"大家咩時候去做gym?","createTime":"2019-02-17T16:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T05:16:26.000Z","uid":195337,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"08524f12c7f0b13d38e20c95765290999542fdc2","tid":1025903,"uid":195337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"成日都好想一早起身做完gym先番工，<br />\n但總係好難起到身，<br />\n覺得早上做gym個人應該會精神啲<br />\n大家又會咩時候去gym room<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又有冇咩方法可以朝早易啲起身而又唔攰?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b17791299b0a9313aa725e9608968e597e9ad1","tid":1025903,"uid":84072,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"七點半（朝頭早）<br />\n<br />\n早啲瞓就可以早啲起身囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c11a1a56e82a56673d383860752c9b162359e11","tid":1025903,"uid":195337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"77b17791299b0a9313aa725e9608968e597e9ad1","tid":1025903,"uid":84072,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"七點半（朝頭早）<br />\n<br />\n早啲瞓就可以早啲起身囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"但早訓上床又訓唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應唔應該搵日超早起身然後逼自己早訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9bc7b48c5f8c49000237edc76b768665894c96","tid":1025903,"uid":84072,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c11a1a56e82a56673d383860752c9b162359e11","tid":1025903,"uid":195337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"77b17791299b0a9313aa725e9608968e597e9ad1","tid":1025903,"uid":84072,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T16:27:00.000Z","msg":"七點半（朝頭早）<br />\n<br />\n早啲瞓就可以早啲起身囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"